00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,192
But my mother went with me
to the hospital.

525
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:31,919
And on the way, she told me

526
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:34,435
that cold
actually increases the pain.

527
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,638
What's needed is warmth.

528
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,480
My mother.

529
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:47,075
She used to sing.

530
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,000
(HUMMING)

531
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:13,471
RA'S: This maybe hard
for you to understand.

532
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:19,078
But I have walked this earth
for centuries...

533
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,797
waiting for you, Bruce.

534
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:24,873
Only you can kill me,

535
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,398
and only with that dagger.

536
00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:30,199
That is my curse.

537
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:33,039
That is the meaning of my vision.

538
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:35,795
I don't believe you.

539
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:39,552
- Believe me.
- This is just another manipulation.

540
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:42,960
See.

541
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:45,760
Look.

542
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:47,789
My true form.

543
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:53,073
Every moment of my life is agony.

544
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:57,955
End my suffering.

545
00:35:00,560 --> 00:35:01,789
Whatever your curse is,

546
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:06,271
you deserve it for what you've done.

547
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:08,750
You're angry, Bruce. I understand.

548
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,112
But unless you strike me down

549
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:13,237
with that blade,
you will never be free.

550
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,320
No!

551
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:17,520
I won't.

552
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:22,356
Then allow me. to tell you
what will happen...

553
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,758
if you don't kill me.

554
00:35:28,680 --> 00:35:29,909
I will disappear.

555
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:33,351
And let you live your life.

556
00:35:34,640 --> 00:35:37,519
You will follow the path of light.

557
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:41,796
Grow into a fine man.
Become a husband.

558
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:44,280
A father.

559
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:48,030
There may be a day when you forget

560
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,079
I ever existed.

561
00:35:53,520 --> 00:35:56,478
But then, I will return.

562
00:35:57,680 --> 00:36:01,560
And I will kill everyone you love.

563
00:36:02,480 --> 00:36:05,120
Just as you watched your parents die.

564
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:09,878
Just as you watched me
slice your friend's throat,

565
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:16,078
I will slaughter your wife
and children before your very eyes

566
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:19,755
and there will be nothing
you can do about it.

567
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:21,560
(GRUNTING AND GASPING)

568
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:24,400
Die.

569
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,960
(SCREAMING)

570
00:36:44,600 --> 00:36:46,113
Yes. (BREATHING HEAVILY)

571
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,040
(INDISTINCT ANNOUNCEMENTS)

572
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:28,829
Are you going to arrest me?

573
00:37:30,400 --> 00:37:31,400
For what?

574
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:34,960
For murder.

575
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,239
I don't know what
I just saw in there.

576
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:38,856
But as far as I'm concerned,

577
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:41,918
Ra's al Ghul's men
broke into Blackgate and he escaped.

578
00:37:44,160 --> 00:37:46,629
I betrayed myself,
and my parents' memory.

579
00:37:49,320 --> 00:37:50,719
I took a life.

580
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:53,318
I did exactly what Ra's said I would.

581
00:37:54,600 --> 00:37:56,736
Just because you know
you're capable of doing something

582
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:58,353
doesn't mean it has to happen again.

583
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:03,630
Bruce, you and I have known
each other a long time.

584
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,752
Since the night your parents
were murdered.

585
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:09,456
Now you may not feel like
you're that kid anymore,

586
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:10,800
but I knowthat you are.

587
00:38:12,200 --> 00:38:13,838
One who believes in doing good.

588
00:38:15,240 --> 00:38:16,514
And fighting for what's right.

589
00:38:18,520 --> 00:38:21,080
Who will do anything
to keep the people he loves safe.

590
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:27,036
Nothing that happened today
changes that.

591
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:41,835
What are you doing?

592
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:43,520
You said it yourself.

593
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:46,560
It's over.

594
00:38:48,200 --> 00:38:49,200
No.

595
00:38:50,120 --> 00:38:52,157
- Can't let you do that, Master Bruce.
- Alfred.

596
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,477
Listen, we started
this vigilante caper

597
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:56,830
to prepare for Ra's return,
didn't we?

598
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,919
It's become so much bigger than that.

599
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:03,240
I see that now, I mean,
I was wrong and you were right.

600
00:39:05,080 --> 00:39:06,400
You can make a difference.

601
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,152
I'm not the hero Gotham needs.

602
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:16,872
I made that decision
the moment I killed Ra's al Ghul.

603
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:20,754
I took the dark path.

604
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:24,560
Yes, you did.

605
00:39:25,640 --> 00:39:28,200
And it's gonna be a long,
bumpyjourney back.

606
00:39:29,800 --> 00:39:34,670
But I believe in you, Master Bruce.
I always have and I... I always will.

607
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:39,150
And I understand
that you don't feel worthy now.

608
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,795
But when you do, this...

609
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:46,915
this will be waiting for you.

610
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,557
As will I, sir.

611
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:15,736
These guys that attacked us.

612
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:17,717
They didn't even have five bucks
between them.

613
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,909
We need a new plan.

614
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:26,800
What?

615
00:40:27,960 --> 00:40:28,960
Truth.

616
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:32,480
Grundy friend know...

617
00:40:33,320 --> 00:40:34,320
Grundy?

618
00:40:36,120 --> 00:40:37,554
You deserve to know...

619
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,915
you and I,

620
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,520
(SIGHS)

621
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:46,031
were the very best of friends.

622
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:48,239
And then something happened to you

623
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:49,816
and Ijust didn't recognize you.

624
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:53,356
But what is important
is that with your muscles,

625
00:40:54,120 --> 00:40:55,235
we can make money.

626
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:59,238
And with money,
we can make me smart again.

627
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:02,117
And then we'II figure out
what happened to you.

628
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,792
Just trust me, okay?

629
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,480
Grundy, come on.

630
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:12,835
(ROCK MUSIC PLAYING)

631
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,680
(PEOPLE CHATTERING AND CHEERING)

632
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:19,960
(PUNCHES THUMPING)

633
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:29,160
(GRUNTING)

634
00:41:30,720 --> 00:41:31,720
Yeah, come on!

635
00:41:45,520 --> 00:41:48,319
What is this? A knitting circle?
Let's see some blood!

636
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:51,480
Hey, I'm looking for the person
in charge here.

637
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,880
You're looking at her.

638
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:56,350
What do you want, squirt?

639
00:41:57,520 --> 00:42:00,399
Well, if there's money to be had,
we'd like to put our hat in the ring.

640
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:01,600
(LAUGHS SARCASTICALLY)

641
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:03,440
And who are you?

642
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:05,115
L'm... Hey!

643
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,400
Come back.

644
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:10,074
I'm this fine gentleman's manager.

645
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:12,990
Trust me, he's a monster.

646
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:16,877
Well, more grist for the mill.

647
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:21,596
We'II get you patched up.
Then We'II talk.

648
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:23,600
Hey!

649
00:42:24,280 --> 00:42:25,280
G0 get the doc.

650
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:29,510
AII right. One, two, three.

651
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:38,439
Hey, doc! Cherry wants you
to come look at some new guy.

652
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,515
WOMAN: I'II be right there.

